{"tid":1185490,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"金獅花園車位143萬沽 1個多月升23萬","createTime":"2019-06-04T09:48:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T10:49:14.000Z","uid":226177,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ece54c8f79dfc569044907094a446107529b8626","tid":1185490,"uid":226177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:48:53.000Z","msg":"車位價回升，投資者短線獲利離場。根據EPRC經濟地產庫資料顯示，大圍金獅花園1期車場L4層單號車位，上月以143萬元沽出。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，原業主於今年4月份以120萬元購入車位，持貨1個月多後沽出，帳面獲利23萬元，升值16%。值得一提是，車位原業主與物業投資者鍾學良同名。其次，北角華曦大廈車場雙號車位，上月以168萬元沽出，原業主2月份以160萬元購入車位，持貨3個月，帳面獲利8萬元離場。<br />\n<br />\n一個月23萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb7017dff88dcde69748ff9446210d7aa03dc38","tid":1185490,"uid":96728,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T15:30:48.000Z","msg":"好奇點解會有人接貨<br />\n果度車位租先2千幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"155ec0c3c242fbc645051d35de2e163d6351d652","tid":1185490,"uid":63212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4eb7017dff88dcde69748ff9446210d7aa03dc38","tid":1185490,"uid":96728,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T15:30:48.000Z","msg":"好奇點解會有人接貨<br />\n果度車位租先2千幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T00:35:55.000Z","msg":"回報好低"},{"pid":"507180fbc4eac09a486480c1b4698b98da72d734","tid":1185490,"uid":29238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4eb7017dff88dcde69748ff9446210d7aa03dc38","tid":1185490,"uid":96728,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T15:30:48.000Z","msg":"好奇點解會有人接貨<br />\n果度車位租先2千幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T01:56:01.000Z","msg":"因為上蓋有將會有大屋苑 而且車位比例好少 仲有個大商場<br />\n金獅果到雖然遠d 但真正既租金係上蓋入左伙先會反映到<br />\n到時可能有3千5左右     但145萬真係好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申無持貨"},{"pid":"cd60812c6421a536de